---
import FeatherMotif from "../shared/FeatherMotif.astro";
---

<section class="world-of-mirador py-24 bg-black relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6 text-center">
            The World of Mirador
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            In 2075, the corporate city-state of Mirador stands as a testament to the
            fusion of technology and human ambition.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <!-- Left side: Description -->
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-jade mb-4">A City of Attention</h3>
                <p class="text-white mb-4">
                    Mirador operates on an attention-based economy where everyone has the
                    tools to broadcast their ideas, but the real challenge is finding
                    anyone who cares to listen.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
                    The city houses various factions with competing visions for the
                    future, from corporate powers like Toltek Industries to the resistance
                    movements challenging the status quo.
                </p>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
                    <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-white/10 rounded-lg">
                        <h4 class="text-teal-400 text-lg font-medium mb-2">
                            Corporate District
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                            Home to Toltek's headquarters and the beating heart of the
                            attention economy.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-black p-4 border border-white/10 rounded-lg">
                        <h4 class="text-amber-400 text-lg font-medium mb-2">
                            The Commons
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">
                            Public spaces where citizens fight for visibility in an
                            overcrowded attention marketplace.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right side: Visual representation -->
            <div class="order-1 md:order-2 flex justify-center">
                <div class="relative w-full max-w-md aspect-square">
                    <!-- Abstract city visualization -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div
                            class="w-4/5 h-4/5 border-2 border-jade/40 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-slow-spin"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="w-3/4 h-3/4 border border-jade/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
                            >
                                <div
                                    class="w-2/3 h-2/3 border border-jade/20 rounded-full"
                                >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Center Element -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <div
                            class="bg-black/80 p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/10 shadow-lg shadow-jade/10"
                        >
                            <FeatherMotif
                                width="100"
                                height="100"
                                color="jade"
                                opacity="0.8"
                                rotate="0"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Orbital elements -->
                    <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 transform translate-x-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-800/30 rounded-full border border-primary-800/50"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 transform -translate-x-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 bg-accent/20 rounded-full border border-accent/40"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Background elements -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 opacity-10">
        <FeatherMotif width="300" height="300" color="white" rotate="180" />
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    @keyframes slow-spin {
        from {
            transform: rotate(0deg);
        }
        to {
            transform: rotate(360deg);
        }
    }

    .animate-slow-spin {
        animation: slow-spin 60s linear infinite;
    }
</style>
